    "description": "Role Summary:\r\nA dynamic team member responsible for leading software development projects in the realm of Python and web applications.\r\nKey Responsibilities: - Designing, developing, testing, deploying, maintaining complex Python-based enterprise solutions using Django framework. - Architecturally design system to be scalable on AWS cloud infrastructure with efficient data management through PostgreSQL database systems. - Collaborate closely with stakeholders and cross-functional teams to ensure alignment of technical implementations with business objectives, adhering strictly to the project timelines and quality standards established by senior leadership or functional managers.,\r\nRequired Qualifications: - Bachelor's or Master's degree in Computer Science, Engineering, Information Technology. Preferably specialization in software development; Python programming experience is a must-have qualification.. - Proven record of at least 3\u20135 years working with object-oriented languages such as Java/Python and frameworks like Django., - Experience developing web applications using AWS cloud services (AWS S3, EC2 etc.) Preferably coupled with background in designing scalable systems. Basic knowledge about PostgreSQL database management is a plus but not mandatory..",
